Rating: 3
These were yummy! I made them just as directed and they had a nice bite. Make sure to heat your pan for a few minutes before adding -- they won't stick. The only drawback is that you have to be careful what you serve them with as they are very strong-flavored -- i.e, don't serve with a delicate fish. Best with grilled meat or chicken.

